&lt;p>Happy Terror/Treat day! This is for my wife whom I&amp;rsquo;m missing very much while she&amp;rsquo;s away for work. This image is inspired by her love of scary fun-things as well as her love of our little ham-star, Misha. I hope you Enjoy!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>